title: Catherine Cohen: A Joke about Pandemic Changes
description: Catherine Cohen jokes about pandemic changes in her Netflix special, "The Twist...? She's Gorgeous". Grab your tickets at NetflixIsAJokeFest.com to see Catherine and your other favorite comedians in the Netflix is a Joke Fest happening April 28th-May 8th in Los Angeles.
